{"tid":1543353,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"跳閘爆閘撞閘本身就有機會比人捉 自己小心係最重要","createTime":"2019-09-05T07:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T10:00:31.000Z","uid":190141,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f5f6a47b81c3437823f7461d6ce2643dd1e2a1e8","tid":1543353,"uid":190141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"琴晚-今朝見突然好多咩便衣狗捉人跳閘之類<br />\n<br />\n先唔理真定假 琴晚我係fb見人手動轉咩太子站有便衣狗捉跳閘 結果我碌極tg連登都無<br />\n<br />\n呢d極有可能係黨鐵派人上黎開post兇鳩大家等大家唔敢跳<br />\n<br />\n係想同大家講番<br />\n<br />\n以跳閘爆閘撞閘尾隨人既方式 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入閘</span></span>前最基本一樣野就係睇附近有冇可疑人/粉紅人<br />\n<br />\n呢個道理同你上街抗爭要blackblock要戴口罩一樣 最基本保護自己既措施黎<br />\n<br />\n前兩日見d人話有防暴係到守都照跳 果d真係玩命比人捉都唔抵可憐<br />\n<br />\n你覺得唔對路咪拍卡入閘<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出閘係唔撚洗驚架</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇可疑人foodpanda你都照樣跳出去撞出去跟人出去捐出去<br />\n<br />\n有人叫你有人拍你就頭也不回咁跑就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係比人捉到再無走到既手段咪唯有罰500<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但罰500果陣記得問撚清楚條友叫咩名 然後投訴佢條含家產 d查飛狗最撚驚人投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 大家記住呢段潮文<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">不要拍咭，去跳閘！人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲！\n嬲黨鐵就去搞牠，喜歡就跳閘啊！拍咭有甚麼用？\n還是會被狗衝入來打，跳不到去就捐，捐不到就去踢，被捉就跑走，大不了罰500咯。\n你連閘都不敢跳，還有甚麼資格說光復香港？\n罰500後繼續跳，跳到黨鐵職員開始懷疑人生，讓他覺得人生的意義就是看著你跳閘。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n今日無跳無撞唔洗灰心 呢個係長期運動黎 同你罷買一樣 今日聽日跳唔到 下星期跳 下星期跳唔到 下個月跳<br />\n<br />\n到你沖破心理關口果陣 你就會後悔自己點解咁撚蠢比多咁多錢 我學生番學一日坐底十蚊車錢 依加每日慳十蚊 跳兩日就夠我食餐加藤屋下午茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72aef3ddcf8373a5c70e8cae229ecf582a64456e","tid":1543353,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:02:36.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"678825b72460670ad5cf98c938594677109abf6b","tid":1543353,"uid":21424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s5.ezgif.com/save/ezgif-5-2a08538c8047.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs5.ezgif.com%2Fsave%2Fezgif-5-2a08538c8047.gif&h=0b45625d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"640c07f0c10c4d0be12f8f323def80decfa03d92","tid":1543353,"uid":213352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wt3BFAh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWt3BFAh.jpg&h=d9e55ce0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6be115c26c5c400a5212f43fc9ccc7cbf6b1096b","tid":1543353,"uid":190141,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"再講多句<br />\n<br />\n我依兩日都係撞閘/跟人出去<br />\n<br />\nd機會響 特別你撞閘佢係會響兩次 (一次係你未拍卡果陣近個閘、第二次係你撞開左之後)<br />\n<br />\n然後響幾大聲下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係完全無人理我</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人以前最撚叻就係各家自掃門前雪架啦 驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158add4dc4b3ad46e348d200e3694e79e81d1f15","tid":1543353,"uid":190141,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:05:34.000Z","msg":"不要拍咭，去跳閘！人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲！嬲黨鐵就去搞牠，喜歡就跳閘啊！拍咭有甚麼用？還是會被狗衝入來打，跳不到去就捐，捐不到就去踢，被捉就跑走，大不了罰500咯。你連閘都不敢跳，還有甚麼資格說光復香港？罰500後繼續跳，跳到黨鐵職員開始懷疑人生，讓他覺得人生的意義就是看著你跳閘。"},{"pid":"b30672b8c1579fbe5ca11ef58d51d7de6475eed8","tid":1543353,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Mo2AMb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Mo2AMb.png&h=fa328dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXr0gH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXr0gH8.jpg&h=f7a79c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c36c7a1241560893a083e744de0575bf9de2c8a8","tid":1543353,"uid":303862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f5f6a47b81c3437823f7461d6ce2643dd1e2a1e8","tid":1543353,"uid":190141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"琴晚-今朝見突然好多咩便衣狗捉人跳閘之類<br />\n<br />\n先唔理真定假 琴晚我係fb見人手動轉咩太子站有便衣狗捉跳閘 結果我碌極tg連登都無<br />\n<br />\n呢d極有可能係黨鐵派人上黎開post兇鳩大家等大家唔敢跳<br />\n<br />\n係想同大家講番<br />\n<br />\n以跳閘爆閘撞閘尾隨人既方式 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入閘</span></span>前最基本一樣野就係睇附近有冇可疑人/粉紅人<br />\n<br />\n呢個道理同你上街抗爭要blackblock要戴口罩一樣 最基本保護自己既措施黎<br />\n<br />\n前兩日見d人話有防暴係到守都照跳 果d真係玩命比人捉都唔抵可憐<br />\n<br />\n你覺得唔對路咪拍卡入閘<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出閘係唔撚洗驚架</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇可疑人foodpanda你都照樣跳出去撞出去跟人出去捐出去<br />\n<br />\n有人叫你有人拍你就頭也不回咁跑就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係比人捉到再無走到既手段咪唯有罰500<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但罰500果陣記得問撚清楚條友叫咩名 然後投訴佢條含家產 d查飛狗最撚驚人投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 大家記住呢段潮文<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">不要拍咭，去跳閘！人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲！\n嬲黨鐵就去搞牠，喜歡就跳閘啊！拍咭有甚麼用？\n還是會被狗衝入來打，跳不到去就捐，捐不到就去踢，被捉就跑走，大不了罰500咯。\n你連閘都不敢跳，還有甚麼資格說光復香港？\n罰500後繼續跳，跳到黨鐵職員開始懷疑人生，讓他覺得人生的意義就是看著你跳閘。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n今日無跳無撞唔洗灰心 呢個係長期運動黎 同你罷買一樣 今日聽日跳唔到 下星期跳 下星期跳唔到 下個月跳<br />\n<br />\n到你沖破心理關口果陣 你就會後悔自己點解咁撚蠢比多咁多錢 我學生番學一日坐底十蚊車錢 依加每日慳十蚊 跳兩日就夠我食餐加藤屋下午茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"